


## 🚀 How to Play
1. Open the game in your browser.  
2. Choose ✊ Rock, ✋ Paper, or ✌️ Scissors.  
3. The computer will randomly select one.  
4. Results will show instantly along with updated scores.  
5. Click **Reset** to restart anytime.


## 🌐 Deployment
This project can be easily deployed using:
https://vaish-navi05.github.io/-Rock-Paper-Scissors-Game/




## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **HTML5** – Structure  
- **CSS3** – Styling & Animations  
- **JavaScript (ES6)** – Game logic  


